com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport

Class LinkComparison

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.CoreItemComparison
      • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.ItemComparison
        • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.LinkComparison

  • public final class LinkComparison
extends ItemComparison
    A kind of ItemComparison that represents the differences between two versions of the same Link.

    Note: LinkComparisons contain no reference to the Entitys at the ends of the Link. Links do not record the versions of the Entitys at their ends, so no meaningful comparison is possible.

    Since:
    2.0

      • LinkComparison

        public LinkComparison(CoreItem olderItem,
                      CoreItem newerItem,
                      boolean deletionChanged,
                      boolean securityChanged,
                      boolean primaryPropertiesChanged,
                      boolean modifiedTimestampChanged,
                      Collection<String> addedCardIds,
                      Collection<String> removedCardIds,
                      Collection<SourceInfoComparison> changedSourceInfos,
                      Collection<CardComparison> changedCards,
                      Collection<String> addedPropertyGroupIds,
                      Collection<String> removedPropertyGroupIds,
                      Collection<String> addedPropertyIds,
                      Collection<String> removedPropertyIds,
                      Collection<String> changedPropertyIds,
                      boolean linkDirectionChanged,
                      boolean linkStrengthChanged)
        Constructs a new LinkComparison.
        Parameters:
        olderItem - The older Link in this LinkComparison.
        newerItem - The newer Link in this LinkComparison.
        deletionChanged - true if one of the Link versions is marked as deleted while the other is not; false otherwise.
        securityChanged - true if the Link versions have different security settings; false otherwise.
        primaryPropertiesChanged - true if the Link versions have different primary properties; false otherwise.
        modifiedTimestampChanged - true if the Link versions have different modified timestamps; false otherwise.
        addedCardIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the newer but not the older Link.
        removedCardIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the older but not the newer Link.
        changedSourceInfos - SourceInfoComparisons describing SourceInfo changes between Cards present on both Links.
        changedCards - CardComparisons describing changes between Cards present on both Links.
        addedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the newer but not the older Link.
        removedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the older but not the newer Link.
        addedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the newer but not the older Link.
        removedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the older but not the newer Link.
        changedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys whose values are different in the two Links.
        linkDirectionChanged - true if the LinkDirections are different between the older and newer Links; false otherwise.
        linkStrengthChanged - true if the LinkStrengths are different between the older and newer Links; false otherwise.
